title: judas Priest - Sin After Sin [320k MP3]
description:
Sin After Sin is the third album by British heavy metal group Judas Priest, released in 1977. It is the first of eleven consecutive Judas Priest albums to be certified gold by the RIAA. It was remastered in 2001 with two bonus tracks added.
